> Could you please clarify how you did this? Which folder do I need to place the sunflare into? I don't see a sunflare file in the OPM and Kopernicus folders, just one in the scatterer folder which I have replaced with Galileo's.
> 

this <abbr title="Module Manager (mod)">MM</abbr> patch will do the trick all by itself

    @Kopernicus:FINAL
    {
      %Body[Sun]
      {
        %ScaledVersion
        {
          %Light
          {
            %sunLensFlareColor = 0, 0, 0, 0
          }
        }
      }
    }

or... not? Hang on. Testing, I thought it was working before.

Ah, fixed it. Needed some % luvin. In fact I just changed them all to % to be safe

